  (116, 3, 'Each figure is labelled with its code. Work out what each letter stands for, then select the code for the final figure.
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 720 146" width="720" height="146" role="img"><rect x="0" y="0" width="720" height="146" fill="#ffffff"/><g transform="translate(54,56)"><rect x="-50" y="-50" width="100" height="100" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(0,-6)"><polygon points="0,-22 22,19 -22,19" fill="#bbbbbb" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2.5"/></g><g transform="translate(0,4)"><polygon points="0,-10 10,0 0,10 -10,0" fill="#111111"/></g><circle cx="0" cy="41" r="5" fill="#111111"/></g><text x="54" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="bold" fill="#111111">B X G</text><g transform="translate(166,56)"><rect x="-50" y="-50" width="100" height="100" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(0,0)"><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="33" fill="#111111" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2.5"/></g><g transform="translate(0,0)"><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="8" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="3.5"/></g><circle cx="0" cy="41" r="5" fill="#111111"/></g><text x="166" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="bold" fill="#111111">C Y G</text><g transform="translate(278,56)"><rect x="-50" y="-50" width="100" height="100" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(0,-6)"><polygon points="0,-33 33,28 -33,28" fill="#bbbbbb" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2.5"/></g><g transform="translate(0,4)"><polygon points="0,-10 10,0 0,10 -10,0" fill="#111111"/></g><circle cx="0" cy="-41" r="5" fill="#111111"/></g><text x="278" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="bold" fill="#111111">B X H</text><g transform="translate(390,56)"><rect x="-50" y="-50" width="100" height="100" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(0,-6)"><polygon points="0,-22 22,19 -22,19" fill="#bbbbbb" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2.5"/></g><g transform="translate(0,4)"><polygon points="-3,-11 3,-11 3,-3 11,-3 11,3 3,3 3,11 -3,11 -3,3 -11,3 -11,-3 -3,-3" fill="#111111"/></g><circle cx="0" cy="41" r="5" fill="#111111"/></g><text x="390" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="bold" fill="#111111">A X G</text><g transform="translate(502,56)"><rect x="-50" y="-50" width="100" height="100" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(0,0)"><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="22" fill="#bbbbbb" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2.5"/></g><g transform="translate(0,0)"><polygon points="-3,-11 3,-11 3,-3 11,-3 11,3 3,3 3,11 -3,11 -3,3 -11,3 -11,-3 -3,-3" fill="#111111"/></g><circle cx="41" cy="0" r="5" fill="#111111"/></g><text x="502" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="bold" fill="#111111">A Y J</text><g transform="translate(650,56)"><rect x="-50" y="-50" width="100" height="100" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(0,0)"><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="33" fill="#bbbbbb" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="2.5"/></g><g transform="translate(0,0)"><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="8" fill="none" stroke="#111111" stroke-width="3.5"/></g><circle cx="0" cy="41" r="5" fill="#111111"/></g><text x="650" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="20" font-weight="bold" fill="#111111">?</text></svg>', '["B Y G", "C Y G", "C Y H", "C Y J"]', 1, 'First letter codes the inner mark (A = cross, C = ring, B = diamond); Second letter codes the outer shape (Y = circle, X = triangle); Third letter codes the dot position (H = N, J = E, G = S). The final figure''s code is C Y G.', false),
  (117, 3, 'Three of these figures are rotations of one figure. Select the one that is most unlike the others.', '["<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 110 110\" width=\"104\" height=\"104\" role=\"img\"><rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"110\" height=\"110\" fill=\"#ffffff\"/><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"104\" height=\"104\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#111111\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><g transform=\"translate(55,55) rotate(180) scale(0.85)\"><g transform=\"translate(0,16) rotate(0) scale(1.6)\"><polygon points=\"0,-17 13,1 6,1 6,17 -6,17 -6,1 -13,1\" fill=\"#111111\" stroke=\"#111111\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></g><g transform=\"translate(28,-20) rotate(0) scale(0.55)\"><polyline points=\"13,-14 -8,-14 -8,0 8,0 8,14 -13,14\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111111\" stroke-width=\"4.5\"/></g><rect x=\"-38\" y=\"-30\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#bbbbbb\" stroke=\"#111111\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></g></svg>", "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 110 110\" width=\"104\" height=\"104\" role=\"img\"><rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"110\" height=\"110\" fill=\"#ffffff\"/><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"104\" height=\"104\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#111111\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><g transform=\"translate(55,55) rotate(225) scale(0.85)\"><g transform=\"translate(0,16) rotate(0) scale(1.6)\"><polygon points=\"0,-17 13,1 6,1 6,17 -6,17 -6,1 -13,1\" fill=\"#111111\" stroke=\"#111111\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></g><g transform=\"translate(28,-20) rotate(0) scale(0.55)\"><polyline points=\"13,-14 -8,-14 -8,0 8,0 8,14 -13,14\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111111\" stroke-width=\"4.5\"/></g><rect x=\"-38\" y=\"-30\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#111111\" stroke=\"#111111\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></g></svg>", "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 110 110\" width=\"104\" height=\"104\" role=\"img\"><rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"110\" height=\"110\" fill=\"#ffffff\"/><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"104\" height=\"104\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#111111\" 